0.9.name: wordpress/bp-better-directories
0.9.description:
Turn your member directories into sophisticated directory filters. Admins can select which profile fields are filterable, and visitors can filter in a slick AJAX interface.

WARNING! This plugin may not scale well! Don't use without decent object caching. WARNING! This plugin is not ready to be used on a production site!
